      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Etape 4\n\nData Analysis",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "KbdxqgITyS6bbKnzV9N9P",
      "originalText": "Etape 4\n\nData Analysis",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "ZFhL0SKmVvwEmQL-I93zB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 393.134621,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 405,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#5b2346",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 339186920,
      "version": 44,
      "versionNonce": 1237381784,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779558696164,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "> Conduct review of\nexisting datasets\n> Determine whether\nproject will produce a\nnew dataset\n> Describe special\narchiving challenges,\nespecially involved\nconsent and\nconfidentiality\n> Identify potential\nusers\n> Determine costs\nrelated to archiving\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "> Conduct review of existing datasets\n> Determine whether project will produce a new dataset\n> Describe special archiving challenges, especially involved consent and confidentiality\n> Identify potential users\n> Determine costs related to archiving\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "87B1LNbC9zq8emuC3AOIs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 693.1346209999999,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 270,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#5b2346",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1504446696,
      "version": 31,
      "versionNonce": 2134302616,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779558696164,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "> Create data\nmanagement plan\n> Make decisions\nabout documentation\nform and content\n> Conduct pre-tests\nand pilot test of\nmaterials and\nmethods\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "> Create data management plan\n> Make decisions about documentation form and content\n> Conduct pre-tests and pilot test of materials and methods\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "ZRPpxVm9nlqata1jWaEMy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 973.1346209999999,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 432,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#5b2346",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 833581976,
      "version": 51,
      "versionNonce": 1231498392,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779558696164,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "> Follow best\npractices\n> For data, address\ndataset integrity,\nvariable names,\nlabels, and groups;\ncoding; missing data\n> For documentation,\nexplore use of DDI\nstandard; include all\nrelevant\ndocumentation\nelements; document\nconstructed variables\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "> Follow best practices\n> For data, address dataset integrity, variable names, labels, and groups; coding; missing data\n> For documentation, explore use of DDI standard; include all relevant documentation elements; document constructed variables\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "5XgAA7e79MwJpDE5zy25y",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1253.134621,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 189,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#5b2346",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2144671464,
      "version": 72,
      "versionNonce": 1644550552,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779558696164,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n> Manage master\ndatasets and work\nfiles\n> Set up appropriate\nfile structures\n> Back up data!",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\n> Manage master datasets and work files\n> Set up appropriate file structures\n> Back up data!",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
